Subject: [PATCH v11 07/22] riscv: mm: Add p?d_leaf() definitions
Date:   Mon,  7 Oct 2019 16:38:07 +0100
Message-Id: <20191007153822.16518-8-steven.price@arm.com>
X-Mailer: git-send-email 2.20.1
